	(text_box "tracks battery state-of-charge using a Coulomb counter plus voltage sensing across a 10mΩ sense resistor. This is what gives you an actual battery percentage rather than just \"charging / not charging.\""
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 231.14 204.47 0)
		(size 55.88 11.43)
