	(text_box "the physical USB-C connector. Wired only for power right now (charging), not data. A handful of ESD diodes (D4-D7) sit on the power/CC lines to absorb static discharge from the exposed port; D1/D3 are the data-line ESD diodes but aren't populated yet since USB data isn't wired up."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 30.48 16.51 0)
		(size 55.88 11.43)
		(margins 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525 0.9525)
