		(uuid "cd6a80e2-7230-44c1-a14e-33f387f95962")
	)
	(text_box " same part family i use for the SIM/SD fix and the soft-power circuit. Here it gates +3.3V → +3.3V_SW, and per J.Wood thesis this is specifically what fully kills power to the display backlight and keypad LEDs, since the earlier board revision couldn't turn them off completely otherwise."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 345.44 148.59 0)
		(size 48.26 13.97)
